nts' and lecturers' preference lists,\nthe probability of such a matching existing is significantly higher if ties are\nrestricted to the lecturers' preference lists.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 20:19:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Nov 2018 16:23:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 5 May 2019 10:15:50 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 15:30:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
