de). This study highlights the need for caution in determining M67\nrotation periods from Campaign 5 data, but this can be extended to other\nclusters observed by K2 and, soon, TESS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 22:10:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 22:28:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-08"}
