ations. Since the WRs represent\nan evolutionary phase directly preceding core-collapse, they are are crucial to\nunderstanding both this process and the nature of the resultant relativistic\nremnants, providing unique constraints on the evolution and death of the most\nmassive stars forming in the local, high metallicity Universe (Abridged).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 May 2018 13:18:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
